Paper: hep-th/9506166

Date: 1995-06-26

Title: On the anomaly of nonlocal symmetry in the chiral QED

Authors: Hyeonjoon Shin, Young-Jai Park, Yongduk Kim, and Won T. Kim

Comments: 4 pages, latex, no figures

Journal-ref: J.Korean Phys.Soc. 29 (1996) 392-393

We show that the anomaly of nonlocal symmetry can be canceled by thewell-known Wess-Zumino acton which cancels the gauge anomaly in thetwo-dimensional chiral electrodynamics.